object.customQuery:
select q.agent_agency, 
w.property_state, 
q.line_of_business, 
w.uuid as workspace_uuid,
q.current_status,
q.quote_type,
q.submission_timestamp,
w.submissionQuoteUuid,
q.uuid as quote_uuid
from dbo.r_quoteinfo q
join dbo.r_workspace w on q.workspace_uuid = w.uuid
order by q.agent_agency, w.property_state, q.line_of_business, w.uuid, q.current_status, q.quote_type
